OL,3,CMeet the woman who has been running
OL,4,Cthe same nursery for 50 years
OL,6,FA nursery is celebrating 50 years
OL,7,Fsince opening with the owner still at
OL,8,Fthe helm now aged 89-years-old.
OL,10,FPamela Edwards opened the Formby Day
OL,11,FNursery, alongside her late husband in
OL,12,F1975, now running it with the help of
OL,13,Fother family members.
OL,15,FPamela says she loves what she does
OL,16,Fand has looked after generations of
OL,17,Fthe same families.
