OL,3,CMeet the woman who has been running
OL,4,Cthe same nursery for 50 years
OL,6,F"When we moved here, there were no
OL,7,Fplaygroups or nurseries at all and
OL,8,Flots of children so we decided we
OL,9,Fwould go for it," she said.
OL,11,F"We started with four children and now
OL,12,Fwe have 46. We have a lot of parents
OL,13,Fthat came here as children. It's like
OL,14,Fone big family really, it's been
OL,15,Flovely."
OL,17,FOver the past five decades, Pamela has
OL,18,Fbeen known as Mrs Edwards but
OL,19,Frecently, she has earned a new special
OL,20,Ftitle courtesy of the children she
OL,21,Fcares for, one that she enjoys.
