OL,3,CMeet the woman who has been running
OL,4,Cthe same nursery for 50 years
OL,6,F"Most of them call me Grandma," she
OL,7,Fadded. "If I go shopping, you hear
OL,8,Feveryone say 'look here's grandma', so
OL,9,Fit's very nice."
OL,11,FKatie Brannan Pamela's granddaughter,
OL,12,Fwho also works at the nursery says her
OL,13,Fdedication and passion is an
OL,14,Finspiration: "It's amazing working
OL,15,Fwith her.
OL,17,F"It's a privilege really, she's got
OL,18,Fsuch a determination. 89 almost 90,
OL,19,Fout doing us every day.
