OL,3,CMeet the woman who has been running
OL,4,Cthe same nursery for 50 years
OL,6,F"She means everything to me, I'm just
OL,7,Fso proud of her and if I am half the
OL,8,Fwoman she is then I'll be proud of
OL,9,Fmyself as well. "
OL,11,FThe 89-year-old is still as present as
OL,12,Fever and has no plans of slowing down
OL,13,Fanytime soon.
OL,15,FWhen asked about retirement she told
OL,16,Fus she had no plans.
