OL,3,CMeet the woman who has been running
OL,4,Cthe same nursery for 50 years
OL,6,F"Well it's my life really," she said.
OL,7,F"I've never thought of doing anything
OL,8,Felse. It's lovely and it's worth it.
OL,9,FAnd I shall keep going, I'm not
OL,10,Fretiring yet."
